ion-to-blogging/#managing-comments'=>'https://wordpress.org/documentation/article/introduction-to-blogging/#managing-comments','https://wordpress.org/documentation/article/introduction-to-blogging/#comments'=>'https://wordpress.org/documentation/article/introduction-to-blogging/#comments','https://wordpress.org/documentation/article/block-themes/'=>'https://wordpress.org/documentation/article/block-themes/','Publish on: %s'=>'Publiseres: %s','Schedule for: %s'=>'Planlegg: %s','Published on: %s'=>'Publisert: %s','Scheduled for: %s'=>'Planlagt: %s','publish box time formatH:i'=>'H:i','publish box date formatM j, Y'=>'j. M Y','The directives (lines) between "BEGIN %1$s" and "END %1$s" are
